<sect1 id="group__physics__cuda_1physics_functions">
<title>Available Functions</title>
<para>The <computeroutput><ref refid="namespacephysics__" kindref="compound">physics_</ref></computeroutput> namespace provides the following functions:</para>
<sect2 id="group__physics__cuda_1physics_momentum">
